-- Canada’s Ivey Index of Purchasing Managers Was 49.0 in June
-- B y   A n d r e w   M a y e d a
-- 2012-07-06T14:00:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-06/canada-s-ivey-index-of-purchasing-managers-was-49-0-in-june.html
Canada’s Ivey purchasing managers’
index was 49.0 in June, following a prior reading of 60.5 in
May, according to a statement on the University of Western
Ontario business school’s website.  Readings of more than 50 indicate purchasing by governments
and companies advanced. Economists surveyed by Bloomberg News
forecast a reading of 57.5, the median of 12 estimates.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andrew Mayeda in Ottawa at 
